{"tid":1659550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「煲大佢」張建宗冀不要再糾纏721事件","createTime":"2019-10-17T04:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T07:37:18.000Z","uid":12919,"like":7,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"0d56e30c5aec9a8506d2756e6e49f6647757ae9f","tid":1659550,"uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"張建宗冀不要再糾纏721事件　又強調青年是未來<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗表示，香港經歷4個多月長的不穩定，是時候好好反思，希望藉今次施政報告的機會，用新思維找出路，強調青年是未來，希望一個都不能少。被問到要求警察道歉是否已成為禁忌詞，張建宗表示，大家要向前走，希望不要再糾纏在721事件，強調維持香港要向前發展、要維穩、要優化和做好現存工作。有公務員致電本台節目，對施政報告無檢討管治問題感到憤怒，亦有市民批評張建宗，回應警暴問題時失信於民<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-17 12:07:02<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486698-20191017.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486698-20191017.htm&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=4df8d160\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486698-20191017.htm&h=d5a89e77\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486698-20191017.htm</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcbE2mx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcbE2mx.png&h=f97762a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c40e2e004882f759891157ece4bfbd31853fb74a","tid":1659550,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:17:17.000Z","msg":"溫馨提示 <br />\n和理非大遊行<br />\n政府從來冇俾過屎<br />\n又要吹風和理非<br />\n又幫林鄭手止暴制亂<br />\n林鄭真係多謝你都嚟唔切<br />\n唔記得818和理非完咗<br />\n畀政府撚狗咁撚<br />\n讚你乖乖仔<br />\n仲要吹風裝都唔帶?<br />\n又想好似929咁樣害啲手足食tg,著短褲打到仆街?"},{"pid":"df6a8a89e8601b73ab4cbc61ee4ab18236373ff5","tid":1659550,"uid":223006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"青年是未來 ...未從大陸過來"},{"pid":"7d1c8358c48cf67aecc3ef55c235e3b8ed6727b0","tid":1659550,"uid":44412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"dllm啦"},{"pid":"