","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXwHWog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXwHWog.jpg&h=82569018&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"941b8297105a8d38a229bedf4b06635eb5ef54db","tid":1659550,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d56e30c5aec9a8506d2756e6e49f6647757ae9f","tid":1659550,"uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"張建宗冀不要再糾纏721事件　又強調青年是未來<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗表示，香港經歷4個多月長的不穩定，是時候好好反思，希望藉今次施政報告的機會，用新思維找出路，強調青年是未來，希望一個都不能少。被問到要求警察道歉是否已成為禁忌詞，張建宗表示，大家要向前走，希望不要再糾纏在721事件，強調維持香港要向前發展、要維穩、要優化和做好現存工作。有公務員致電本台節目，對施政報告無檢討管治問題感到憤怒，亦有市民批評張建宗，回應警暴問題時失信於民<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-17 12:07:02<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486698-20191017.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486698-20191017.htm&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=4df8d160\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486698-20191017.htm&h=d5a89e77\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486698-20191017.htm</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcbE2mx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcbE2mx.png&h=f97762a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"That was not fair!!!<br />\nLooking forward is good and is NOT an exclusive event. <br />\nYou can look forward AND find out who those gangsters were.<br />\nThe latter is a legal responsibility.<br />\nHe was dead wrong !!"},{"pid":"984cf8bf6600a1d30d757bb84fb5a1abde36b24f","tid":1659550,"uid":169108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:15:31.000Z","msg":"721市民被黑社會襲擊<br />\n身為政府官員唔下令徹查<br />\n竟然話唔好深究 咩世界"}]}